header.gameNote: ACC/BIG TEN CHALLENGE PRESENTED BY CONTINENTAL TIRE

videos.description: Jalen Carey swings it to Elijah Hughes, who rises up and knocks down a long triple to give the Orange a 24-21 lead over the Buckeyes.
videos.headline: Syracuse takes lead on Hughes' deep 3

videos.description: Luther Muhammad dishes to Kyle Young, who loses his grip on the ball as he tries to dunk, but somehow manages to finesse it home through contact for the and-1.
videos.headline: Young can't finish dunk, gets and-1 anyway

videos.description: Jalen Carey kicks it ahead to Elijah Hughes, who attacks the rim and banks in a layup through contact for the 3-point play.
videos.headline: Hughes runs floor for fast-break and-1

videos.description: Elijah Hughes comes off a screen and knocks down a huge 3-pointer, extending the Orange lead to 52-45 over the Buckeyes.
videos.headline: Hughes heats up with pull-up triple

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods gets undercut on a 3-pointer, but it doesn't stop him from hitting the shot and cutting into the Buckeyes' lead with a 4-point play.
videos.headline: Woods connects from deep for 4-point play

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods comes up with the Syracuse turnover and kicks it ahead to C.J. Jackson, who flies in for the finish and ends up in the seats.
videos.headline: Jackson ends up in front row after fast-break finish

videos.description: Kyle Young tries to finish inside, but Paschal Chukwu rises up to pin his shot on the backboard and preserve the 64-58 Syracuse lead late in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Chukwu protects rim with huge block
